{
  "stem": "3964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, of course, the price was dictated by, by the government, what we could sell it for. 1937-- from 1936 to 1937, I didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in 1937, the middle of the year, a school was opened up in a town near Frankfurt, Bad Nauheim.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This school was to serve children like myself and approximately 250 other children in the general area where I lived in the Kassel district who couldn't go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this became a Jewish school, where some of us who live closed enough to-- but now I would commute every day-- and others who lived further away, like I did, were staying at this school overnight during the school year.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, of course, during the vacation time we would go home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister at the time experienced the same hardships I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously, when Bad Nauheim school opened up, she went also to Bad Nauheim.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Bad Nauheim, school education was excellent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of our teachers were young teachers who had just graduated from the teacher seminar in Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was some older teachers who had been teachers in the German elementary and higher schools of learning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they couldn't teach there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Consequently, they needed a place to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were teaching in our schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the staff we had was excellent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the experience I had in Bad Nauheim was an excellent experience, which, to this day, is still with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still fondly think of the days in Bad Nauheim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number one, we weren't harassed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were amongst Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
